  <brief_title>Diet and Activity in Cerebral Palsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>DIET, ACTIVITY AND MEDICAL CO-MORBIDITIES IN ADOLESCENTS and ADULTS WITH CEREBRAL PALSY: WHAT ARE THE EFFECTS ON THE METABOLIC PROFILE?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
