  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to fill a gap in the literature, identify relevant clinical measures, and
      provide insight into the independent modifiable risk factors of obesity in the CP population
      with the long-term goal of improving screening, management and prevention of obesity in this
      at-risk and underserved population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
